---
// MultiCloudProscons.astro — Multi-cloud tradeoffs
---
<div class="mcp-wrap">
  <h3 class="mcp-title">Multi-Cloud — The Honest Tradeoffs</h3>
  <div class="mcp-grid">
    <div class="mcp-col mcp-col--pro">
      <span class="mcp-hl mcp-hl--green">Actual Benefits</span>
      <div class="mcp-item">Avoid single-vendor lock-in (negotiation leverage)</div>
      <div class="mcp-item">Best-of-breed per service (BigQuery + AWS Lambda)</div>
      <div class="mcp-item">Regulatory/data residency requirements</div>
      <div class="mcp-item">M&A — acquired company uses different cloud</div>
    </div>
    <div class="mcp-col mcp-col--con">
      <span class="mcp-hl mcp-hl--red">Real Costs</span>
      <div class="mcp-item">2-3x operational complexity</div>
      <div class="mcp-item">Teams need expertise in multiple clouds</div>
      <div class="mcp-item">Cross-cloud networking is expensive and slow</div>
      <div class="mcp-item">Data egress charges ($0.08-0.12/GB)</div>
      <div class="mcp-item">Lowest common denominator architecture</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mcp-verdict"><strong>Honest take:</strong> Most teams don't need multi-cloud. They think they want it for "redundancy" but end up with 2x the complexity and half the velocity. Multi-cloud makes sense for large enterprises with regulatory requirements or genuine best-of-breed needs. For everyone else, go deep on one cloud.</div>
</div>
<style>
  .mcp-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0;border:1px solid #334155}
  .mcp-title{color:#f1f5f9;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 1.5rem}
  .mcp-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;margin-bottom:1rem}@media(max-width:600px){.mcp-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .mcp-col{padding:14px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.2);border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #334155}
  .mcp-col--pro{border-top:2px solid #4ade80}.mcp-col--con{border-top:2px solid #f87171}
  .mcp-hl{display:block;font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;font-family:monospace;margin-bottom:8px}.mcp-hl--green{color:#4ade80}.mcp-hl--red{color:#f87171}
  .mcp-item{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.7rem;line-height:1.7;padding-left:10px;position:relative}.mcp-item::before{content:'→';position:absolute;left:0;color:#475569}
  .mcp-verdict{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.72rem;line-height:1.6;padding:10px 14px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.15);border-radius:8px;border-left:3px solid #f59e0b}.mcp-verdict strong{color:#f59e0b}
</style>
